Gold_SQL_query: select short_name from node_table where num_rows >= 10 or num_cols >= 10

NL_query: Show the top 10 directories that contain the most subdirectories.
Gold_SQL_query: select t1.short_name, count(*) from node_directory as t1 join edge_has_dir_dir as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id group by t1.short_name, t2.source_node_id order by count(*) desc

NL_query: List names and descriptions of all databases in the lake.
Gold_SQL_query: select short_name, description from node_database

NL_query: Calculate the sum of all file sizes belonging to each owner account.
Gold_SQL_query: select t1.node_id, t1.short_name, sum(t3.fsize) from node_owner as t1 join edge_own as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id join node_file as t3 on t2.target_node_id = t3.node_id group by t1.node_id, t1.short_name

NL_query: List the modified time of the 'date' classification label.
Gold_SQL_query: select modified_date from node_classification where short_name = 'date'

NL_query: How many columns are associated with each label that has 'nyc' as a prefix?
Gold_SQL_query: select t1.short_name, count(*) from node_label as t1 join edge_assoc as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id group by t1.node_id, t1.short_name having t1.short_name like 'nyc%'

NL_query: Which tables contain the word 'weight' in their names a column that contains the word 'building' in it's name?
Gold_SQL_query: select t1.short_name from node_table as t1 join edge_has_table_col as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id join node_column as t3 on t2.target_node_id = t3.node_id where t1.short_name like '%weight%' and t3.short_name like '%building%'

NL_query: List ids for directories that contain more than 20 immediate subdirectories.
Gold_SQL_query: select source_node_id from edge_has_dir_dir group by source_node_id having count(*) > 20

NL_query: How many files does each owner account possess?
Gold_SQL_query: select t1.node_id, t1.short_name, count(*) from node_owner as t1 join edge_own as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id join node_file as t3 on t2.target_node_id = t3.node_id group by t1.node_id, t1.short_name

NL_query: Sort the nosql databases in the lake by their last modified date.
Gold_SQL_query: select short_name from node_nosql order by modified_date desc

NL_query: Which columns have at least one business term associated with them?
Gold_SQL_query: select distinct t1.short_name from node_column as t1 join edge_assoc_term_col as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.target_node_id

NL_query: Print all records for the dbo internet sales table.
Gold_SQL_query: select * from node_table where short_name = 'fact_internet_sales'

NL_query: Show the short name, long name and description for the modification column in the bill of materials table.
Gold_SQL_query: select t3.short_name, t3.long_name, t3.description from node_table as t1 join edge_has_table_col as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id join node_column as t3 on t2.target_node_id = t3.node_id where t1.short_name = 'bill_of_materials' and t3.short_name = 'mod_date'

NL_query: List all string columns created in the past 3 days.
Gold_SQL_query: select short_name, creation_date from node_column where col_type = 'string' and creation_date >= now() - interval '3 days'

NL_query: Show the creation date and description for the column named 'ccid'.
Gold_SQL_query: select creation_date, description from node_column where short_name = 'ccid'

NL_query: Find all tables with the term 'eph' or 'employee_pay_history' in it's name.
Gold_SQL_query: select short_name from node_table where short_name like '%eph%' or short_name like '%employee_pay_history%'

NL_query: List creation timestamps for directories with size greater than 100Kb.
Gold_SQL_query: select short_name, creation_date from node_directory where dsize > 100

NL_query: Print names for all directories that were created in the past day.
Gold_SQL_query: select short_name, creation_date from node_directory where creation_date >= now() - interval '24 hours'

NL_query: Show the number of related assets for each asset.
Gold_SQL_query: select t1.short_name, count(*) from node as t1 join edge as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id group by t1.short_name

NL_query: Display the name, long name, description and last modification date for the document owner column?
Gold_SQL_query: select short_name, long_name, description, modified_date from node_column where short_name = 'doc_owr'

NL_query: Show the column names and descriptions for all columns in the 'prospective_buyer' report table.
Gold_SQL_query: select t3.short_name, t3.description from node_table as t1 join edge_has_table_col as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id join node_column as t3 on t2.target_node_id = t3.node_id where t1.short_name = 'prospective_buyer'

NL_query: Find all columns associated with the classification 'enterprise'.
Gold_SQL_query: select t3.node_id, t3.short_name from node_classification as t1 join edge_assoc_class_col as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id join node_column as t3 on t2.target_node_id = t3.node_id where t1.short_name = 'enterprise'

NL_query: Show long name and description for the start date column in the bill of materials table.
Gold_SQL_query: select t3.long_name, t3.description from node_table as t1 join edge_has_table_col as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id join node_column as t3 on t2.target_node_id = t3.node_id where t1.short_name = 'bill_of_materials' and t3.short_name = 's_date'

NL_query: Find the mean size of a file for each folder?
Gold_SQL_query: select t1.node_id, t1.short_name, avg(t3.fsize)  from node_directory as t1 join edge_has_dir_file as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id join node_file as t3 on t2.target_node_id = t3.node_id group by t1.node_id, t1.short_name

NL_query: List all people who own one or more databases in the lake.
Gold_SQL_query: select distinct t1.short_name from node_owner as t1 join edge_own as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id join node_database as t3 on t2.target_node_id = t3.node_id

NL_query: How many assets of each type id does each user account own?
Gold_SQL_query: select t1.node_id, t1.short_name, t3.type_id, count(*) from node_owner as t1 join edge_own as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id join node as t3 on t2.target_node_id = t3.node_id group by t1.node_id, t1.short_name, t3.type_id

NL_query: List creation timestamps for all folders.
Gold_SQL_query: select short_name, creation_date from node_directory

NL_query: Who are the top 10 people who own the most assets? How many assets each own?
Gold_SQL_query: select t1.short_name, count(*) from node_owner as t1 join edge_own as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id group by t1.short_name, t2.source_node_id order by count(*) desc limit 10

NL_query: What are the tables can be unioned with each table in the lake?
Gold_SQL_query: select t1.short_name from node_table as t1 join edge_unionable_table_table as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id

NL_query: When was the last time that each directory was modified?
Gold_SQL_query: select short_name, modified_date from node_directory

NL_query: List the extension, creation date and last modified date for all files in the lake.
Gold_SQL_query: select short_name, creation_date, modified_date from node_file

NL_query: Count the number of joinable relationships found for each table in the past 13 days.
Gold_SQL_query: select t1.short_name, count(*) from node_table as t1 join edge_joinable_table_table as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id where t2.creation_date >= now() - interval '13 days' group by t1.node_id, t1.short_name
